<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If validation rule refers only one field (or all fields using wildcard metacommand) and field value is an array, then Zend_Filter_Input::_validateRule() iterates through it and applies validators to an array values.</p>

<p>So, it's not possible to validate arrays.</p>

